                "comment": "He is one of the best professors I've had at this school. He is incredibly witty and super interesting. Him and Professor Caldwell are a great team and both work at the Mendota Mental Health Institute and I loved listening to their stories. Quizzes are fairly easily if you show up to lecture and listen. I would take this class again in a heartbeat!",
