            {
                "comment": "Super interesting class! If you attend class, the quizzes will be easy. The whole grade is based on four 40-question quizzes. Funny guys!",
                "difficulty_rating": 2,
                "quality_rating": 4
            },
            {
                "comment": "Psych 401 is fascinating and enjoyable if you let the class structure be a little chaotic. Greg cares a lot about the topics and sometimes his lectures are boring, but his personality makes it significantly more enjoyable. Mike who he co-teaches with is a fantastic lecturer- This class has almost 0 homework, 4 heavy exams, and don't skip class!",
                "difficulty_rating": 3,
